### Recommendation compare
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/recommend/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "U100",
  "top_k": 20,
  "query": "AI regulation"
}

### Strategy evaluation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/evaluate/strategies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "k_values": [5, 10, 20]
}

### Hybrid RAG query
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/me/rag/hybrid-query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "新闻推荐系统为什么需要推荐透明度？",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Agent trace
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/me/agent/trace
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "结合我的资料库，推荐并解释几篇 AI 监管相关的新闻",
  "top_k": 5
}
